author: dannas
msg: Start notifying about prop changes in the 'svn patch' code.
With this change, we're making a notification for every path that has
prop changes. BUT, we don't yet check for rejected prop hunks so every
path that the patch says has property changes will be reported as updated.
The correct behaviour will be implemented one step at a time.
(notify): Print a ' U' char for updated properties.
(send_patch_notification): Check if there are changes to
props or files before setting content_state.
